  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Company
    Partner company of LivePrint.
    ControlPanel
    Control Panel for companies to create/update/delete links.
    CreateLink
    Create Link page.
    Data
    Contains the data of the app.
    Demo
    Demo class for the inspection process based on LivePrint.
    Funcs
    General-use static functions for the app.
    Link
    Pair of photo and video files that a company submitted to LivePrint.
    Login
    Implements login for companies.
    LPHome
    Home Page of the LivePrint section of the app.
    LPList
    Allows the user to specify the company they are using LivePrint for.
    MainActivity
    Entry-point into the app.
    NatTreasureHunt
    Home Page of the National Treasure Hunt section of the app.
    Question
    Stores a grouping of a resource name, a question about that resource, and possible answers to that question.
    Register
    Implements registration for companies.
    TestActivity
    Used for in-app testing purposes.
    UpdateLink
    Allows companies to update the data of a link.
